title: Joe Flacco Trade, Antonio Brown latest with John Breech (Football 2/14)
description:
Will Brinson and John Breech dive into the big news of the day, with Joe Flacco being traded by the Ravens to the Broncos (3:00), breaking down what it means for Denver, what it means for Flacco and what it means for Case Keenum. Then the guys examine the Antonio Brown situation (30:00) and where he could be headed in 2019 and look at the crop of free agent QBs out there.
